 beverages from across the globe and including descriptions of the experience of tasting each drink, this book offers an accessible and comprehensive exploration of the scientific dimensions of spirits.  aMode of access: Internet via World Wide Web.  aIn English.0 aDescription based on online resource; title from PDF title page (publisher's Web site, viewed 29. Mai 2023) 0aLiquorsxHistory. 7aSOCIAL SCIENCE / Agriculture & Food (see also POLITICAL SCIENCE / Public Policy / Agriculture & Food Policy).2bisacsh1 aTattersall, Ian, eauthor.4aut4http://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/aut1 aWynne, Patricia J., econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertEBOOK PACKAGE COMPLETE 2022 Englishz978311099389908iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertEBOOK PACKAGE COMPLETE 2022z9783110994810oZDB-23-DGG08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertEBOOK PACKAGE Political Science 2022 Englishz978311099451308iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertEBOOK PACKAGE Political Science 2022z9783110994407oZDB-23-PLW08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertYale University Press Complete eBook-Package 2022z97831107497790 cprintz978030025515740uhttps://doi.org/10.12987/9780300265101?locatt=mode:legacy40uhttps://www.degruyter.com/isbn/9780300265101423Coveruhttps://www.degruyter.com/document/cover/isbn/9780300265101/original  a978-3-11-074977-9  Yale University Press Complete eBook-Package 2022b2022  a978-3-11-099389-9  EBOOK PACKAGE COMPLETE 2022 Englishb2022  a978-3-11-099451-3  EBOOK PACKAGE Political Science 2022 Englishb2022  aEBA_UCA_YUP  aGBV-deGruyter-alles  aZDB-23-DGGb2022  aZDB-23-PLWb2022  aZDB-23-UCY